You are forecasting which spare parts will fail or run low in the next 14-30 days at the Toyota Boshoku Bawal plant.

Last 180 days of spare-part consumption: {{ JSON.stringify($('Q: Consumption (180d)').all().map(x => x.json)) }}

Last 90 days of breakdowns (maintenance tickets): {{ JSON.stringify($('Q: Recent Breakdowns').all().map(x => x.json)) }}

Last 90 days of recovery action patterns: {{ JSON.stringify($('Q: Recovery Patterns').all().map(x => x.json)) }}

Return up to 10 forecasts (most urgent first). For each, predict the failure date, urgency, and recommended quantity to order.

Return JSON: {forecasts: [{part_id, part_name, machine_id, predicted_failure_date (YYYY-MM-DD), days_until_failure, confidence (0..1), reasoning (one sentence), recommended_action, order_quantity, urgency (critical|high|normal)}]}
